-- Toyota: floormat recall is only for United States
-- 
-- Tue Sep 29, 2009 8:57pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/09/30/us-toyota-japan-sb-idUSTRE58T03520090930

 

 TOKYO  (Reuters) - Toyota Motor Corp said on Wednesday that the floormat recall the world's largest carmaker issued overnight only affects the United States. 

 The floormats in which a defect has been reported are only used in vehicles sold in the United States, a Toyota spokesman said. (Reporting by Yumiko Nishitani)